	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Fetid Hide Drape drops off of a level 65 Rogue named Assassin Kakoo. His max hit against the MA was 669, but he had a nasty 2k damage proc, which he seemed to fire quite often, accompanied by the following text: &quot;You legs buckle and bleed, you have taken 2000 points of damage!&quot;. &quot;You legs&quot;? Looks like someone needs to proof-read... and then change the wis to int.<br><br>Immune to changes in attack speed (slows). Snared with Festering Darkness. Killed with 1 full group having our shaman and druid assisting the cleric with healing.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Jan 18 00:10:24 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
